1. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper deals with cellular automata, which is a topic in discrete mathematics. 
2. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The problem of injectivity of the global function of a cellular automaton is a computational complexity problem. 
3. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) - The paper uses logical reasoning to prove the undecidability of the problem. 
4. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) - Cellular automata have applications in game theory, and the paper may have implications for game theory. 
5. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The hyperbolic plane is a topic in computational geometry, and the paper deals with cellular automata in this context.
